Executive: Achcha aapka haan dekh sakte ho incoming calls ka. Nahi mam jaisa main dekh pa raha hu aap video call se connect ho payenge us pe video meet pe, jaisa main dekh pa raha hu isme to dikha raha hai.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Mere mere end pe mam actually aapka jo problem hai na wo jo hai wo to dikha raha hai aapne abhi recent mein Omni OMNI se aapne contact kiya hai kabhi? And Soheb se kiya hai, Ashok Kumar se?

Executive: Kya mam?
Customer: Meet call, meet call.
Executive: Okay okay main aapko connect karta hu. Uh ek minute aapko abhi deta hu main.
Executive: Mam dekhna aapke mail pe link aaya hoga.

Customer: Hello?

Customer: Nahi ho raha sir.

Customer: Nahi nahi sir Mjahan.

Customer: Haan M small M J A N Jahan 18355@gmail.com.

Executive: Hello?
Executive: Ek minute mam hold rakhna. Mam. Haan. Mam maine link share kar diya mam.

Executive: Ji mam. Hello? Haan ji mam link aapko whatsapp pe mila? Aapne whatsapp pe.
Executive: Koi baat nahi mam whatsapp pe join kar sakte hai mam agar whatsapp pe agar hum whatsapp pe share kare to link. Haan kar sakte hai. Theek hai aap ye link copy karke. Abhi bhej dijiye mujhe isi number pe.

Customer: Haan hi aaya hai.
